{"tid":2375653,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"華春瑩: 歐洲議會部分議員混淆是非　敦促摒棄雙重標準","createTime":"2021-01-22T07:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T09:17:31.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"427dd1dccdb7075ab247c85b6b52c766fefba551","tid":2375653,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:42:35.000Z","msg":"歐洲議會通過有關香港的決議，譴責北京中央政府打壓香港民主派，要求歐盟對中國內地與香港相關人員實施制裁。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人華春瑩回應時表示，歐洲議會部分議員混淆是非，顛倒黑白，推動通過決議，是對中國香港事務和中國內政的粗暴干涉，中方表示堅決反對，強調香港事務純屬中國內政，根本不是民主人權問題，任何外國政府組織和個人都無權干預。<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩表示，中方敦促歐洲議會正視香港已經回歸中國的現實，恪守國際法和國際關係的基本準則，摒棄雙重標準，停止充當別國的「人權教師」，切實尊重中國的主權和香港法治，停止以任何形式干預香港事務，干涉中國內政。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571811-20210122.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571811-20210122.htm&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TZhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=cb8727dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571811-20210122.htm&h=69ac7322\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571811-20210122.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2cd38f3dce7bae19cbd0af9e6e9b966c1ebdb054","tid":2375653,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e90251ebedfefe7d106f7a4aaf2e21d0ce44a6","tid":2375653,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:44:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7aaff90c5ed3f3531ab9efe4366a392a0d7c8f","tid":2375653,"uid":79562,"like":6,"dislike"